org.cloudgraph.store.mapping

Class UserDefinedField

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cloudgraph.store.mapping.KeyField
      • org.cloudgraph.store.mapping.UserDefinedField

  • public class UserDefinedField
extends KeyField
    The settings for one user-defined field within a composite row-key. Each user defined field maps a property within the data graph to a position within the composite row key, adding another "dimension" to the key. In HBase for example, this user defined composite row-key approach enables the HBase partial row-key scan functionality which greatly improves query performance.

    Java class for UserDefinedField complex type.
